{"tid":1971662,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭叫你「同舟共濟」 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-04-14T05:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T05:37:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a38a77754945c0cfaeed2adc56b77619c9680f4a","tid":1971662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200414/20899354/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200414%2F20899354%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B80yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=022e1cb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200414%2F20899354%2F&h=6f718e5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200414/20899354/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭叫你「同舟共濟」 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200414/large/1586757344_83ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586757344_83ef.jpg&h=cdbf989c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌神唱過「04祝福你」，沒想到今天卻陷入了「林鄭祝福你」的陷阱。好好一個「同舟共濟online演唱會」，卻被林鄭一個「祝福」弄得波濤洶湧、差點翻艇。急得阿旦開show前拍片解畫&hellip;&hellip;應該是「解毒」，其實就是告訴各方：我阻唔到有人出post，但我們是保持社交距離的。<br />\n<br />\n要有甚麼樣的特首，才會出一個post「撐你」卻變成「害你」？看到開show前林鄭出post的那個詭異笑容，胃口倒盡，罵聲四起。<br />\n<br />\n我可以原諒林鄭出post抽水呃like，畢竟政府請的那個「小編」人工實在太高，140多萬的年薪，不多出一兩個post無法交代；但我無法忍受林鄭那句留言：「請特別記住『同舟共濟』中的這句歌詞：『香港是我家，怎捨得失去它。』」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭和你講「同舟共濟」，就像穿皮草的貴婦和你講「愛護動物」，本身就是兇手，卻一臉慈悲流眼淚。香港搞到今天如斯田地，不就是你林鄭的功勞嗎？由「反修例」風波開始，每一個行動，林鄭都在破壞、拆毀「香港這個家」。縱容警暴、政治僭越疫情、拒絕封關&hellip;&hellip;她說「怎捨得失去它」時，不會慚愧嗎？<br />\n<br />\n看看歌神演唱會直播的留言，多少人大喊「林鄭下台」、「光復香港」，又有多少人聽到「同舟共濟」的時候，搖頭嘆息「回不去了﹗香港已經不是歌神那個年代的香港了。」<br />\n<br />\n我們坐在這條船，如何「齊齊令它不遭破損」？每一下的警棍都在打爛這隻船，疫情已經把香港糟蹋得生死存亡奄奄一息，這個叫人「同舟共濟」的政府卻繼續打壓黃店、追擊傳媒、為難議員，然後「好官我自為之」的在會議室觀賞歌神show，再「很聰明」的補一句「我地有豁免」﹗<br />\n<br />\n「我與你同坐這條船，無情浪把它猛捲」，當日香港遭遇的是「外來風浪」，船上人只要齊心仍有希望；今天船隻遇到凶險，卻是由掌舵的船長造成，你叫人如何接受這種船長的「祝福」？ <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2671c4074032d0c86e696b918852482ecb8f7614","tid":1971662,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"同心抗疫 抵抗暴政 解散黑警 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e882d6f57aac16e0f3c5556660f532bdc90fbee6","tid":1971662,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同舟共制？<br />\n<br />\n當我傻西！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span></span>"}]}